    &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2021/6/8/22523944/lightroom-classic-indesign-illustrator-m1-mac-native-version"&gt;Continue reading&amp;hellip;&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;

</content>
